Interface ScenarioReader

    public interface ScenarioReader

      • readJavaScenario

        List<Scenario> readJavaScenario(Path path,
                                List<JavaArgumentTerm> javaArgumentTermList)
        Reads a java scenario from the file at the specified path and parses its content to retrieve a list of Scenario objects.
        Parameters:
        path - the Path to the file containing the scenario
        javaArgumentTermList - the Argument list of the stepFunction
        Returns:
        a list of Scenario objects parsed from the file, or an empty list if an error occurs
